    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Seven of thirteen credibility factors were assessed and met their required levels. The assessment team accepted the package based on the assessed factors alone. The five unassessed factors (numerical solver error, use error, model form, model inputs, equivalency of input parameters) were noted as deferred items but no formal gap justification or compensating evidence was provided. The decision was recorded as Accepted without documentation of how the unassessed factors at MRL-5 affect overall credibility confidence.",
